  "title": "Retail Sales Representative 门店销售员",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>AGT Global Technology Pte Ltd operates retail outlets specializing in Chinese medicine, health supplements, and wellness products, serving local customers with trusted products and personalized service.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>As a Retail Sales Representative, you will engage with customers to provide product information, handle sales transactions, and support store operations to ensure a positive shopping experience.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and assist walk-in customers by providing clear, friendly, and professional service to meet their needs</li><li>Respond to customer product enquiries and offer basic recommendations to help customers make informed choices</li><li>Promote Chinese medicine, health supplements, and wellness products to increase customer awareness and sales</li><li>Process cashiering duties accurately, including handling payments and issuing receipts</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and organize the retail outlet to create a welcoming shopping environment</li><li>Replenish stock and arrange product displays to ensure shelves are well-stocked and visually appealing</li><li>Support daily store operations and complete ad-hoc tasks as assigned to maintain smooth store functioning</li><li>Work independently and collaboratively with team members to achieve store goals</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to communicate in English; proficiency in Mandarin or dialects is an advantage for effective customer engagement and product explanation</li><li>Willingness to learn about Chinese medicine and health products to enhance customer support</li></ul>",
